			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">Visiting the Kraken at Home</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Researchers have captured what might be the first known recording of a colossal squid living freely in its natural habitat.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/evert-lindquist/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Evert Lindquist</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
					<aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Wordcount</h3>
						May 27, 2024 | 1,200 words, about 6 minutes
					</aside>

					
